{
  "stem": "11611.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we overlapped in one respect.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rasche was a member of the so-called Himmler kreis-- kreis being the German word meaning circle, which we translated as friends of Himmler.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Lyons and Flick, I think, also had connections.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were some other people-- Keppler, Wilhelm Keppler, who was in and around the economic of party affairs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Lyons was working up some kind of charges against the members of the circle of Himmler.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my defendant, Rasche, was a part of or on the fringes of that circle, so we overlapped, and I got to know Charlie Lyon very well.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were on very good terms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe-- I know-- I might have work on them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just don't remember that clearly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know that nobody said prepare an indictment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a piece of an overall indictment for the whole Ministries Case, which ran on page after page.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Late-- I'm trying to remember because it's getting a little hazy at this point.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think it was the latter part of 1948 that the cases actually began in court, although we had had what amounted to kind of deposition hearings, commission hearings of witnesses long before that, probably beginning in the spring of '48, you know, off an on.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The defense would propose to produce some witnesses, and we'd have a hearing before some court commissioner.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those were useful in the trial record.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were in effect kind of sub-testimony in the case.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Consecutively.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I must have been two, three weeks in court.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For all of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The actual court proceedings were a very small part of my work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All day.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember spending three, four days cross-examining Rasche, and maybe a couple days with Kehrl, and appearing there for episodic appearances.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
